    <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/html5shiv/3.7.2/html5shiv.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/respond/1.4.2/respond.min.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <header class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 ">
            <nav class="col-sm-9 col-sm-push-3">
                <ul class="nav inline">
                    {{#if user}}
                        <li><span class="username">Welcome, <strong>{{user.name}}</strong></span></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="avatar"><img src="{{user.avatar}}" class="round"></a></li>
                        <li><a href="/logout" class="round">Deconectează-te</a></li>
                    {{else}}
                        <li><a href="/auth/facebook" class="round icon-user"> Intră în cont</a></li>
                    {{/if}}
                    <li><a href="/about" class="round">Despre</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="round">Distribuie</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
            <a class="col-sm-3 col-sm-pull-9" href="/"><img class="logo" src="/images/logo-colored.png" alt="Iasi Communities Guide Logo"></a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
            <p>Aduce mai aproape oameni	cu	aceleași interese și pasiuni.<br/>Sprijină dezvoltarea comunităților	locale.</p>
            <p>
                Te interesează	un	domeniu anume?	Colecționezi	diverse	lucruri?
                Sau pur și simplu ai	o	pasiune	aparte?	Atunci trebuie doar să
                <strong>găsești</strong> comunitatea	care	ți	se	potrivește și să <strong>te alături</strong>.
                Indiferent	de	domeniu.	Iar dacă	nu	există deja,	<strong>creează</strong> tu una.
                Vei avea surpriza să găsești	o	mulțime	de	alți pasionați ca	tine.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12">
            <div class="start-container clearfix">
                {{#if user}}
                    <button class="default no-border" onclick="window.location.href='communities/new'">Crează o comunitate</button>
                {{else}}
                    <button class="default no-border" disabled>Crează o comunitate</button>
                    <span class="logged-in">Trebuie să fii conectat</span>
                {{/if}}
                <span>sau</span>
                <div class="search-input">
                    <input type="search" placeholder="Caută o comunitate..." id="quicksearch">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-12">
            <div class="filters">
                <span class="filter">Caută în funcție de domeniu:</span>
                <ul class="unstyled-list inline">
                    <li><a class="round grey active" data-filter="*">Toate domeniile</a></li>
                    <li><a class="round technology" data-filter=".filter-technology">Tehnologie</a></li>
                    <li><a class="round management" data-filter=".filter-management">Management</a></li>
                    <li><a class="round creative" data-filter=".filter-creative">Creație</a></li>
                    <li><a class="round fun" data-filter=".filter-fun">Distracție</a></li>
                    <li><a class="round educational" data-filter=".filter-educational">Educație</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-12">
            <div class="sorts">
                <span class="sort">Afișează în funcție de:</span>
                <ul class="unstyled-list inline">
                    <li><a class="round grey active" data-sort="original-order">Ordinea originală</a></li>
                    <li><a class="round grey" data-sort="interest">Domeniu</a></li>
                    <li><a class="round grey" data-sort="alphabetical">A-Z</a></li>
                    <li><a class="round grey" data-sort="members">Număr de Susținători</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <main class="isotope">
        <div class="row">
            {{#each communities}}
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 community {{#each this.categories}}filter-{{this}} {{/each}}" data-interest="{{#each this.categories}}{{this}},{{/each}}" data-members="{{math this.leaders.length '+' this.members.length}}">
                <input class="communityId" type="hidden" value="{{this._id}}">
                    {{#if this.logoURL}}
                    <div class="community-visual" style="background: url('{{this.logoURL}}'), no-repeat;background-size: cover; background-position: center center; background-color: white;">
                    {{else}}
                    <div class="community-visual">
                    {{/if}}
                        <ul class="unstyled-list inline community-tags">
                            {{#each this.categories}}
                                <li><span class="tag bg-{{this}}">{{this}}</span></li>
                            {{/each}}
                        </ul>
                        <ul class="unstyled-list community-members">
                            {{#if this.leaders}}
                                <li><a class="community-leader" href="{{this.leaders.0.profileUrl}}"><img class="round" src="{{this.leaders.0.avatar}}"></a></li>
                            {{else}}
                                <li><a class="community-leader" href="{{this.members.0.profileUrl}}"><img class="round" src="{{this.members.0.avatar}}"></a></li>
                            {{/if}}
                            {{#if this.leaders.length}}
                                {{#if this.members.length}}
                                    <li><a class="community-counter">+{{math (math this.members.length "+" this.leaders.length) "-" 1}}</a></li>
                                {{else}}
                                    {{#if (math this.leaders.length "-" 1)}}
                                        <li><a class="community-counter">+{{math this.leaders.length "-" 1}}</a></li>
                                    {{/if}}
                                {{/if}}
                            {{else}}
                                {{#if this.members.length}}
                                    {{#if (math this.members.length "-" 1)}}
                                        <li><a class="community-leader" href="{{this.members.0.profileUrl}}"><img class="round" src="{{this.members.0.avatar}}"></a></li>
                                        <li><a class="community-leader" href="{{this.members.0.profileUrl}}"><img class="round" src="{{this.members.1.avatar}}"></a></li>
                                        <li><a class="community-leader" href="{{this.members.0.profileUrl}}"><img class="round" src="{{this.members.2.avatar}}"></a></li>
                                        <li><a class="community-leader" href="{{this.members.0.profileUrl}}"><img class="round" src="{{this.members.3.avatar}}"></a></li>
                                        <li><a class="community-counter">+{{math this.members.length "-" 1}}</a></li>
                                    {{/if}}
                                {{/if}}
                            {{/if}}
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="community-content">
                        <div class="fixed-height">
                            <h3 class="community-name" onclick="window.location.href = '/communities/{{this._id}}'">{{this.title}}</h3>
                            <p class="community-desc">{{this.desc}}</p>
                        </div>
                        <button class="default" onclick="window.location.href = '/communities/{{this._id}}'">Află mai multe</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            {{/each}}
        </div>
        <div class="no-results" style="display: none;">Scuze, nu s-a găsit niciun rezultat.</div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-4">
                <h2>Iași<br/>Communities<br/>Guide</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-2 col-sm-offset-6">
                <a class="back-top pull-right" href="#">Sus</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</div>

